# Build output. Every build emits `<project dir>/<name>/<name>.out` (plan-46-D
# §4.1); `*.out` matches at any depth, so it covers both the new output
# directories and stale pre-change artifacts sitting at the project root. The
# output directory's `vendor/` copies are removed by the test harness — they are
# not ignored by pattern, because a binding author's *source* `vendor/` blobs are
# tracked.
*.out

